 all of Physics in under 15 minutes.\nExplaining all of physics would take more than 14 minutes. \nObviously I can't get ALL of physics in that small timeframe, but I tried my best to get all of the stuff worth knowing for most people, and explaining it as simply as possible, as fast as possible ;)\n\nTimestamps:\n00:00 Classical Mechanics\n02:33 Energy\n04:40 Thermodynamics\n06:01 Electromagnetism\n08:30 Nuclear Physics 1\n09:28 Relativity\n11:25 Nuclear Physics 2\n12:13 Quantum Mechanics\n\nThis video took way too many hours to make. \nIf you like it, show it to your friends. Thanks\n\nMusic by Audionautix.com\n\nInspired by Arvin Ash's Video:    • All physics explained in 15 minutes (worth...  ","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":60,"length":48,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CMICEM2rARgBIhMI0vvIiK2ckQMVi3RPBB0NTj0MygEE-O-KBQ==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"/watch?v=5iTOphGnCtg\u0026pp=0gcJCR0AztywvtLA","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_WATCH","rootVe":3832}},"watchEndpoint":{"videoId":"5iTOphGnCtg","startTimeSeconds":0,"playerParams":"0gcJCR0AztywvtLA","watchEndpointSupportedOnesieConfig":{"html5PlaybackOnesieConfig":{"commonConfig":{"url":"https://rr4---sn-o5t5uxa-pncd.googlevideo.com/initplayback?source=youtube\u0026oeis=1\u0026c=WEB\u0026oad=3200\u0026ovd=3200\u0026oaad=11000\u0026oavd=11000\u0026ocs=700\u0026oewis=1\u0026oputc=1\u0026ofpcc=1\u0026msp=1\u0026odepv=1\u0026id=e624cea611a70ad8\u0026ip=124.109.43.196\u0026initcwndbps=1181250\u0026mt=1764590480\u0026oweuc="}}}}}},"onTapOptions":{"accessibilityInfo":{"accessibilityLabel":"YouTube Channel Link: GENERAL CHEMISTRY explained in 19 Minutes"}}},{"startIndex":145,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CMICEM2rARgBIhMI0vvIiK2ckQMVi3RPBB0NTj0MSPncosODlKKFZMoBBPjvigU=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbFZNSVFRWmY2d0dRRDc0MDkxSmRNSm5SblVaZ3xBQ3Jtc0tsbUhHTzBZZnpl